                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-197-18441125 t18441125-197-punishment-157"></join>Confined Three Months</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">ADJOURNED TO THE 16TH OF DECEMBER</hi>, 1844.</p>
